1
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:10,940
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:14,900
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:17,580
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,580
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,980 --> 00:00:25,460
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:29,260
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:31,580
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:35,420
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,100
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:44,420
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:50,820
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:54,980
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:05,660
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,980 --> 00:01:12,460
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:17,460
=Episode 1=
(This story is entirely fictional)

17
00:01:17,460 --> 00:01:18,900
(I transmigrated
as a live-in son-in-law.)

18
00:01:20,620 --> 00:01:21,660
(Divorce Letter)
(Kicked out on day one.)

19
00:01:21,660 --> 00:01:23,820
(Sign the divorce papers today.)

20
00:01:23,820 --> 00:01:24,860
(With enemies closing in...)

21
00:01:25,540 --> 00:01:27,220
(The Zhou family's
Rustling Silk craft was lost.)

22
00:01:27,220 --> 00:01:28,460
(The technique manual)

23
00:01:28,460 --> 00:01:31,060
(was destroyed in a fire ten years ago.)

24
00:01:31,060 --> 00:01:33,060
(I restore ancient methods with science)

25
00:01:35,100 --> 00:01:36,380
(and master the business game.)

26
00:01:36,380 --> 00:01:37,420
68.8 taels?

27
00:01:38,300 --> 00:01:38,860
No.

28
00:01:39,180 --> 00:01:41,180
Only 19.8 taels!

29
00:01:41,180 --> 00:01:42,420
- I'll take it!
- Me too!

30
00:01:44,260 --> 00:01:44,940
Li Yunhe.

31
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:45,580
(Disgracing the elite.)

32
00:01:45,580 --> 00:01:46,140
I won't let you get away with this!

33
00:01:46,140 --> 00:01:47,220
Kneel!

34
00:01:47,220 --> 00:01:48,660
(Raging for my beloved.)

35
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:50,900
(Watch how I)

36
00:01:50,900 --> 00:01:52,420
(turn the tables against all odds.)

37
00:01:53,940 --> 00:01:55,700
(Zhou's Dyehouse)

38
00:01:55,700 --> 00:01:56,460
My lady!

39
00:01:56,460 --> 00:01:57,660
Bad news, my lady!

40
00:01:57,860 --> 00:01:58,300
My lady!

41
00:01:58,300 --> 00:01:59,300
Good news!

42
00:01:59,300 --> 00:02:00,460
Wonderful news!

43
00:02:02,420 --> 00:02:04,020
(Zhou Xingyu, the Zhou heiress)

44
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:04,700
(Zhou Xingyu, the Zhou heiress)
My lady!

45
00:02:04,700 --> 00:02:05,820
Something terrible happened, my lady!

46
00:02:05,820 --> 00:02:07,340
No. It's great news.

47
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:09,540
What's all this fuss about?

48
00:02:09,540 --> 00:02:10,460
He signed it.

49
00:02:10,740 --> 00:02:11,580
He signed?

50
00:02:15,220 --> 00:02:16,420
Who the hell did this?

51
00:02:16,420 --> 00:02:16,780
Huh?

52
00:02:17,540 --> 00:02:18,500
(Song Huaijin, Zhou Xingyu's cousin)

53
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:20,780
(Li Yunhe, the Zhou live-in son-in-law)
Who are you?

54
00:02:21,260 --> 00:02:22,940
On your wedding night
as the live-in groom,

55
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:24,620
you actually snuck off to a brothel?

56
00:02:28,100 --> 00:02:29,180
(I can't remember.)

57
00:02:29,500 --> 00:02:30,500
(I just transmigrated,)

58
00:02:30,500 --> 00:02:31,940
(and I'm already being framed.)

59
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:34,100
(The original owner of this body
was indeed Li Yunhe,)

60
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:36,500
(betrothed to the Zhou heiress
before birth.)

61
00:02:36,940 --> 00:02:37,700
(His family fell,)

62
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:38,980
(so he was taken in
as a live-in son-in-law.)

63
00:02:38,980 --> 00:02:40,340
(On the wedding night,
they got him drunk)

64
00:02:40,340 --> 00:02:41,460
(and dragged him to a brothel.)

65
00:02:43,980 --> 00:02:45,420
Given your misconduct...

66
00:02:45,940 --> 00:02:46,980
Give him the divorce letter.

67
00:02:47,260 --> 00:02:48,260
Divorce letter?

68
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:51,700
Li Yunhe, you must
sign the divorce letter today.

69
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:54,820
Wait.

70
00:02:55,180 --> 00:02:55,980
Hold on.

71
00:02:56,380 --> 00:02:57,500
Don't you think

72
00:02:57,500 --> 00:02:59,780
I was set up?

73
00:03:00,820 --> 00:03:02,620
(This man was a real scumbag.)

74
00:03:02,620 --> 00:03:04,380
(No wonder he got dumped.)

75
00:03:04,900 --> 00:03:06,220
(But since I just transmigrated,)

76
00:03:06,460 --> 00:03:08,260
(I have to fight for myself.)

77
00:03:08,580 --> 00:03:10,780
(Divorce Letter)
Sir, just sign it.

78
00:03:10,780 --> 00:03:12,540
Ms. Zhou's being more than generous

79
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:14,140
by offering you money as compensation.

80
00:03:15,420 --> 00:03:16,300
Money?

81
00:03:16,300 --> 00:03:17,100
Yeah.

82
00:03:20,900 --> 00:03:23,180
(Divorce Letter)

83
00:03:25,500 --> 00:03:27,260
It's not really about the money.

84
00:03:27,660 --> 00:03:28,140
After all,

85
00:03:28,140 --> 00:03:29,860
I'm new here.

86
00:03:29,860 --> 00:03:31,260
I do need some starting capital.

87
00:03:31,660 --> 00:03:32,780
But don't worry.

88
00:03:32,940 --> 00:03:34,540
Once I rise again,

89
00:03:35,100 --> 00:03:36,340
I'll be sure to take good care of...

90
00:03:38,540 --> 00:03:39,860
Hey!

91
00:03:39,860 --> 00:03:41,300
Where's the money you promised me?

92
00:03:41,420 --> 00:03:42,300
Wait!

93
00:03:44,780 --> 00:03:46,300
How could you do this?

94
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:47,620
He was clearly framed last night.

95
00:03:47,820 --> 00:03:49,620
Li Yunhe is worthless.

96
00:03:49,820 --> 00:03:52,100
You're the most beautiful woman
in Feng City.

97
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:55,060
Taking him in
just because of a childhood engagement?

98
00:03:55,220 --> 00:03:56,460
You're getting
the short end of the stick.

99
00:03:57,220 --> 00:03:58,540
This is absurd!

100
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:00,620
Wait! My lady, where are you going?

101
00:04:00,700 --> 00:04:01,980
I haven't signed yet,
so it doesn't count.

102
00:04:01,980 --> 00:04:03,860
(Zhou Manor)

103
00:04:03,860 --> 00:04:04,780
Being a live-in son-in-law

104
00:04:05,340 --> 00:04:06,820
means living under someone else's roof,

105
00:04:07,740 --> 00:04:09,020
always treading carefully.

106
00:04:10,740 --> 00:04:12,060
Maybe being divorced is for the best.

107
00:04:12,820 --> 00:04:14,020
At least I'll have some peace.

108
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:17,020
(It's fine. I won't walk alone.)

109
00:04:17,020 --> 00:04:20,020
(The world will soon know my name.)

110
00:05:20,940 --> 00:05:21,740
(This woman)

111
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:23,540
(is the most beautiful girl
I've ever seen.)

112
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:24,860
(Judging by her clothes,)

113
00:05:25,300 --> 00:05:26,580
(she looks like a servant.)

114
00:05:26,980 --> 00:05:28,460
Stop staring at me.

115
00:05:28,460 --> 00:05:29,660
Answer me.

116
00:05:29,660 --> 00:05:31,260
Are you leaving?

117
00:05:31,540 --> 00:05:32,660
You...

118
00:05:32,940 --> 00:05:33,980
You know me?

119
00:05:35,380 --> 00:05:36,540
Forget it.

120
00:05:36,940 --> 00:05:37,980
It doesn't matter.

121
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:39,300
Wait!

122
00:05:40,660 --> 00:05:41,740
What did you just say?

123
00:05:42,100 --> 00:05:43,260
You don't recognize me?

124
00:05:45,580 --> 00:05:46,380
(Could it be)

125
00:05:46,380 --> 00:05:47,460
(that he's lost his memory?)

126
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:49,980
(Li Yunhe, you're such a scumbag.)

127
00:05:49,980 --> 00:05:51,060
(On the night you married in,)

128
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:52,500
(not only did you stay at a brothel,)

129
00:05:52,780 --> 00:05:53,620
(but you were also involved)

130
00:05:53,620 --> 00:05:55,100
(with a servant girl
from the Zhou household.)

131
00:05:56,860 --> 00:05:57,660
Here's the thing.

132
00:05:58,500 --> 00:05:59,940
I've been divorced now.

133
00:06:00,780 --> 00:06:01,500
Though you're

134
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:03,180
a servant of the Zhou family,

135
00:06:03,180 --> 00:06:04,300
I'll never

136
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:06,740
abandon you and let you down.

137
00:06:06,740 --> 00:06:08,060
Just wait for me a while.

138
00:06:08,380 --> 00:06:09,500
I'll definitely come for you.

139
00:06:09,940 --> 00:06:11,220
Servant?

140
00:06:11,700 --> 00:06:12,540
Me?

141
00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:14,300
(This man)

142
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:16,100
(owed this beautiful girl so much.)

143
00:06:16,380 --> 00:06:18,300
(I can only make it up
with everything I have.)

144
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:20,540
(He really seems to have lost
his memory.)

145
00:06:21,260 --> 00:06:22,980
(But he said he won't abandon me.)

146
00:06:23,700 --> 00:06:24,740
(Interesting.)

147
00:06:24,980 --> 00:06:27,860
(Let me see what game he's playing.)

148
00:06:30,340 --> 00:06:31,140
Don't worry.

149
00:06:31,540 --> 00:06:33,020
The day I return to the Zhou family,

150
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:35,260
I'll come back for you in grand style.

151
00:06:43,180 --> 00:06:44,220
Hey, wait.

152
00:06:44,220 --> 00:06:45,380
Let me see you out.

153
00:06:58,260 --> 00:07:00,420
What's going on?

154
00:07:00,420 --> 00:07:01,220
Oh my god.

155
00:07:04,940 --> 00:07:05,860
Let's go.

156
00:07:12,740 --> 00:07:13,460
Li Yunhe!

157
00:07:13,460 --> 00:07:14,460
Get out here!

158
00:07:14,460 --> 00:07:14,940
Think you deserve to live

159
00:07:14,940 --> 00:07:16,180
with Feng City's top beauty?

160
00:07:16,540 --> 00:07:16,940
No way!

161
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:18,460
Oh my.

162
00:07:18,460 --> 00:07:19,180
That's right!

163
00:07:19,180 --> 00:07:20,620
Why should the city's number one beauty

164
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:21,660
lower herself to be with you?

165
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:23,380
You don't deserve her, you know?

166
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:25,180
What's all this?

167
00:07:25,180 --> 00:07:26,420
Heard you spent the night at a brothel.

168
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:27,700
Come out and fight me if you dare!

169
00:07:27,700 --> 00:07:29,340
Feng City's top beauty?

170
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:30,980
I have to say, you Feng City folks

171
00:07:30,980 --> 00:07:32,540
have some strange taste.

172
00:07:33,460 --> 00:07:34,700
Speaking of top beauties,

173
00:07:35,580 --> 00:07:36,780
I think...

174
00:07:37,100 --> 00:07:37,540
You...

175
00:07:37,940 --> 00:07:38,940
You're quite pretty.

176
00:07:39,220 --> 00:07:40,460
Still want to leave?

177
00:07:40,860 --> 00:07:42,740
Now that I've been divorced,

178
00:07:42,740 --> 00:07:44,740
I definitely can't stay
at the Zhou Manor.

179
00:07:44,900 --> 00:07:46,300
But if I go out there,

180
00:07:46,540 --> 00:07:48,300
there's a whole pack of simps waiting.

181
00:07:48,900 --> 00:07:49,460
Oh man.

182
00:07:49,460 --> 00:07:51,540
This is a total disaster of a start.

183
00:07:51,860 --> 00:07:52,420
Alright now.

184
00:07:52,420 --> 00:07:53,780
I'll handle it.

185
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:57,540
Hey, you...

186
00:07:59,060 --> 00:08:00,020
What's all the racket?

187
00:08:00,460 --> 00:08:02,340
(Zhou Manor)
Throwing things in broad daylight?

188
00:08:02,340 --> 00:08:03,180
How disgraceful!

189
00:08:05,540 --> 00:08:07,100
You dare show your face?

190
00:08:07,100 --> 00:08:08,260
Get him!

191
00:08:10,460 --> 00:08:11,260
Hold on.

192
00:08:12,940 --> 00:08:14,740
I'm the Zhou family's son-in-law.

193
00:08:14,740 --> 00:08:17,380
You dare beat me up
right at the Zhou Manor's gate?

194
00:08:17,380 --> 00:08:18,980
What gave you the nerve to do that?

195
00:08:18,980 --> 00:08:20,060
Boy,

196
00:08:20,260 --> 00:08:21,460
are you still dreaming

197
00:08:21,460 --> 00:08:23,540
that you're part of the Zhou family?

198
00:08:23,540 --> 00:08:24,420
Have a reality check.

199
00:08:24,660 --> 00:08:26,180
Scum like you who fled to a brothel

200
00:08:26,180 --> 00:08:27,700
on his wedding night?

201
00:08:27,700 --> 00:08:29,380
Why wouldn't I dare hit you?

202
00:08:30,180 --> 00:08:31,980
You guys keep yelling.

203
00:08:31,980 --> 00:08:33,060
How do you know

204
00:08:33,060 --> 00:08:34,220
I'm not worthy of Ms. Zhou?

205
00:08:34,700 --> 00:08:36,540
I know Ms. Zhou is clever.

206
00:08:42,100 --> 00:08:44,420
But the Zhou family
is huge and prosperous.

207
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:47,540
Having someone like you
disgrace the family,

208
00:08:47,540 --> 00:08:48,820
(Lu Qifeng, Marquis of Zhennan's son)

209
00:08:48,820 --> 00:08:51,700
(Lu Qifeng, Marquis of Zhennan's son)
where does the Zhou's honor go?

210
00:08:53,980 --> 00:08:54,900
Well, well.

211
00:08:55,220 --> 00:08:56,820
Quite the spectacle.

212
00:08:57,300 --> 00:08:58,580
And who might you be?

213
00:08:59,900 --> 00:09:01,700
Lu Qifeng, the heir

214
00:09:01,980 --> 00:09:02,980
of the Marquis of Zhennan.

215
00:09:04,100 --> 00:09:04,940
If I were you,

216
00:09:05,700 --> 00:09:07,060
I'd leave this place
as soon as possible.

217
00:09:07,700 --> 00:09:09,300
Some things

218
00:09:09,300 --> 00:09:11,060
are not for people like you to touch.

219
00:09:11,620 --> 00:09:12,540
What now?

220
00:09:12,540 --> 00:09:14,140
Don't tell me you're also after

221
00:09:14,140 --> 00:09:15,820
the title of Zhou family's
live-in son-in-law?

222
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:17,580
Aren't you afraid

223
00:09:17,580 --> 00:09:18,900
of bringing shame

224
00:09:18,900 --> 00:09:19,620
to the Marquis House?

225
00:09:19,900 --> 00:09:21,980
How dare you speak to Mr. Lu like that?

226
00:09:21,980 --> 00:09:22,980
Get him!

227
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:24,780
Hold it.

228
00:09:26,580 --> 00:09:28,220
At least you care about appearances.

229
00:09:29,180 --> 00:09:30,580
I just think

230
00:09:30,580 --> 00:09:32,420
killing you at the Zhou Manor's gate

231
00:09:33,300 --> 00:09:34,460
would ruin the scenery.

232
00:09:35,820 --> 00:09:37,260
Wise words, Mr. Lu.

233
00:09:38,420 --> 00:09:39,220
Buddy,

234
00:09:39,980 --> 00:09:41,220
what dynasty is this now?

235
00:09:41,980 --> 00:09:43,380
You don't even know

236
00:09:43,380 --> 00:09:44,420
the Daqian Dynasty?

237
00:09:44,700 --> 00:09:46,420
You're truly an illiterate waste.

238
00:09:47,460 --> 00:09:48,580
Our mighty Daqian

239
00:09:48,580 --> 00:09:49,700
has laws.

240
00:09:50,380 --> 00:09:51,500
You keep babbling about getting someone

241
00:09:51,500 --> 00:09:52,300
and killing someone here.

242
00:09:52,980 --> 00:09:54,420
Where's the justice?

243
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:56,620
Where's the law?

244
00:09:57,380 --> 00:09:58,820
You are illiterate!

245
00:09:58,820 --> 00:09:59,660
You don't actually think

246
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:00,620
you have any talent, do you?

247
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:01,900
I won't waste words

248
00:10:01,900 --> 00:10:03,300
with an uneducated fool like you.

249
00:10:03,540 --> 00:10:05,260
Playing the scholar now, huh?

250
00:10:05,260 --> 00:10:06,260
Do you think

251
00:10:06,260 --> 00:10:07,660
Ms. Zhou is interested

252
00:10:07,660 --> 00:10:09,940
in anyone else's talent but mine?

253
00:10:10,540 --> 00:10:12,380
What do you take yourself for?

254
00:10:12,580 --> 00:10:14,660
You dare call yourself a scholar?

255
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:16,980
How about

256
00:10:16,980 --> 00:10:18,100
I test you?

257
00:10:18,780 --> 00:10:20,020
(Since when did I)

258
00:10:20,020 --> 00:10:21,540
(ever fancy your talent?)

259
00:10:21,700 --> 00:10:24,700
(Daqian's Poet Laureate)
Mr. Lu, this guy must be on something.

260
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:25,500
(Daqian's Poet Laureate)
He's overestimating himself.

261
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:26,580
(Daqian's Poet Laureate)
Go ahead and crush him.

262
00:10:28,900 --> 00:10:29,700
Fine.

263
00:10:30,740 --> 00:10:32,220
I'll give you a verse.

264
00:10:32,620 --> 00:10:33,580
If you can match it,

265
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:35,700
I'll let you leave.

266
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:37,500
And if you lose, what's the penalty?

267
00:10:37,500 --> 00:10:39,060
How could I possibly lose?

268
00:10:39,300 --> 00:10:40,420
Among scholars,

269
00:10:40,420 --> 00:10:42,740
no one reigns supreme.

270
00:10:42,740 --> 00:10:44,140
How do you know you wouldn't lose?

271
00:10:52,700 --> 00:10:54,340
If you win,

272
00:10:55,020 --> 00:10:56,900
the 100 taels here is yours.

273
00:10:57,140 --> 00:10:58,060
Deal!

274
00:10:58,060 --> 00:10:58,780
It's settled.

275
00:10:58,780 --> 00:11:00,140
Give me the verse.

276
00:11:00,540 --> 00:11:02,060
Listen closely.

277
00:11:02,380 --> 00:11:04,020
My first line is:

278
00:11:04,020 --> 00:11:07,700
A man, a plan, a canal, Panama.

279
00:11:08,140 --> 00:11:09,540
(Daqian's Poet Laureate)
That's easy.

280
00:11:09,740 --> 00:11:12,340
(Daqian's Poet Laureate)
A man, a plan, a canal, Panama...

281
00:11:14,860 --> 00:11:18,460
A man, a plan, a canal, Panama?

282
00:11:20,940 --> 00:11:22,060
Read backwards,

283
00:11:22,060 --> 00:11:24,380
that verse is the same.

284
00:11:24,380 --> 00:11:26,660
It's brilliant.

285
00:11:29,340 --> 00:11:30,580
Flowers bloom...

286
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:35,660
Sunrise, moonfall...

287
00:11:40,260 --> 00:11:40,900
How about this?

288
00:11:40,900 --> 00:11:42,580
Whoever can match it,

289
00:11:43,100 --> 00:11:44,860
I'll reward them with 100 taels.

290
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:47,340
100 taels?

291
00:11:47,660 --> 00:11:48,500
Hand over the money,

292
00:11:48,580 --> 00:11:49,780
and I'll definitely match it for you.

293
00:11:52,580 --> 00:11:53,740
Coming out here

294
00:11:54,060 --> 00:11:55,780
brings me 100 taels?

295
00:11:56,100 --> 00:11:57,660
So, my verse?

296
00:12:00,420 --> 00:12:01,820
Listen carefully.

297
00:12:02,380 --> 00:12:03,860
My first line is:

298
00:12:03,860 --> 00:12:07,060
A man, a plan, a canal, Panama.

299
00:12:09,620 --> 00:12:10,660
My matching line is:

300
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:18,420
Able was I ere I saw Elba.

301
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:21,500
So perfectly matched!

302
00:12:23,220 --> 00:12:24,020
Huh?

303
00:12:24,620 --> 00:12:25,700
Whose side are you on?

304
00:12:26,380 --> 00:12:28,380
My mistake, Mr. Lu.

305
00:12:30,180 --> 00:12:31,020
Well?

306
00:12:32,500 --> 00:12:33,420
Want to keep playing?

307
00:12:33,540 --> 00:12:34,860
Go on.

308
00:12:34,860 --> 00:12:35,740
Fine.

309
00:12:35,740 --> 00:12:37,460
Listen closely then.

310
00:12:37,780 --> 00:12:39,260
My first line is:

311
00:12:39,260 --> 00:12:43,100
Smoke veils the pond-side willow.

312
00:12:43,260 --> 00:12:45,460
Smoke veils the pond-side willow?

313
00:12:45,460 --> 00:12:46,060
What's that?

314
00:12:46,060 --> 00:12:46,700
Shut up.

315
00:12:46,700 --> 00:12:49,340
This verse hides the five elements.

316
00:12:50,660 --> 00:12:51,700
Let me think.

317
00:12:52,980 --> 00:12:54,700
(Daqian's Poet Laureate)
Don't tell me you can't match it again.

318
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:00,660
Mr. Lu,

319
00:13:00,980 --> 00:13:02,540
we're just having a bit of fun.

320
00:13:02,740 --> 00:13:03,860
If you can't match it,

321
00:13:03,860 --> 00:13:05,660
at least don't get yourself
so worked up.

322
00:13:05,860 --> 00:13:06,660
Guys,

323
00:13:06,660 --> 00:13:08,780
you should take Mr. Lu Home

324
00:13:08,780 --> 00:13:09,660
before he embarrasses himself further.

325
00:13:09,820 --> 00:13:10,300
You...

326
00:13:11,500 --> 00:13:12,460
Mr. Li won.

327
00:13:12,540 --> 00:13:13,460
He won?

328
00:13:13,860 --> 00:13:15,180
So that's all Lu Qifeng can do?

329
00:13:15,540 --> 00:13:16,780
I was worried for nothing.

330
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:20,180
Don't get too cocky.

331
00:13:20,180 --> 00:13:21,620
So what if you can match verses?

332
00:13:21,700 --> 00:13:22,220
Guys!

333
00:13:22,220 --> 00:13:23,180
Beat him up!

334
00:13:23,300 --> 00:13:24,100
Hey!

335
00:13:24,300 --> 00:13:25,100
Stop!

336
00:13:26,900 --> 00:13:28,700
You have some nerve!

337
00:13:28,700 --> 00:13:29,740
How dare you attack

338
00:13:29,740 --> 00:13:30,980
the Zhou's son-in-law at our gate!

339
00:13:31,260 --> 00:13:32,580
Well, hey, Chunxiang.

340
00:13:32,580 --> 00:13:33,780
This guy is too...

341
00:13:34,340 --> 00:13:35,300
Mr. Zhang,

342
00:13:35,300 --> 00:13:36,580
you'd better behave yourself.

343
00:13:37,220 --> 00:13:37,580
Sir,

344
00:13:37,940 --> 00:13:38,900
please return to the manor with me.

345
00:13:38,900 --> 00:13:39,420
Ah,

346
00:13:39,420 --> 00:13:40,380
sure thing.

347
00:13:41,500 --> 00:13:42,700
See that?

348
00:13:43,100 --> 00:13:44,780
I'm still the Zhou family's son-in-law.

349
00:13:45,300 --> 00:13:46,620
Goodbye now.

350
00:13:46,780 --> 00:13:47,060
You...

351
00:13:47,460 --> 00:13:47,700
You...

352
00:13:51,380 --> 00:13:52,420
This is outrageous!

353
00:13:57,180 --> 00:13:58,980
(Daqian's Poet Laureate)
I wanted to win her over with talent

354
00:13:59,780 --> 00:14:00,580
and leave behind a tale

355
00:14:00,580 --> 00:14:02,500
of a brilliant scholar and a beauty
in Feng City.

356
00:14:04,100 --> 00:14:05,780
Since she refuses to take the hint,

357
00:14:07,980 --> 00:14:09,940
I won't hold back.

358
00:14:09,940 --> 00:14:12,020
And I'll show no mercy.

359
00:14:13,620 --> 00:14:14,400
Understood.

360
00:14:15,860 --> 00:14:17,500
Send some men to Zhou's Fabrics.

361
00:14:18,980 --> 00:14:19,780
Have them spread the word

362
00:14:19,780 --> 00:14:21,500
that they're selling fakes
as quality goods.

363
00:14:21,780 --> 00:14:23,060
I'll make sure the Zhou family

364
00:14:23,180 --> 00:14:24,860
loses all reputation.

365
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:27,460
Come and see, everyone!

366
00:14:27,860 --> 00:14:30,140
Zhou's Fabrics is selling fakes!

367
00:14:30,140 --> 00:14:31,140
(Zhou's Fabrics)

368
00:14:34,820 --> 00:14:35,860
What nonsense are you spouting?

369
00:14:35,860 --> 00:14:37,620
I personally supervised

370
00:14:37,620 --> 00:14:38,780
every batch of silk here,

371
00:14:38,780 --> 00:14:40,220
including the dyeing and sun-drying.

372
00:14:40,220 --> 00:14:41,420
There can't be any fakes.

373
00:14:41,580 --> 00:14:42,380
Who are you?

374
00:14:42,780 --> 00:14:44,100
Judging by your clothes,

375
00:14:44,100 --> 00:14:45,860
you must be
a hired hand of the Zhou family.

376
00:14:46,460 --> 00:14:48,340
How can you represent the Zhou family?

377
00:14:48,660 --> 00:14:50,180
Your shop sells this junk,

378
00:14:50,180 --> 00:14:51,180
so you have to pay compensation.

379
00:14:51,180 --> 00:14:52,860
Get the person in charge out here!

380
00:14:52,860 --> 00:14:54,260
I am the one in charge.

381
00:14:58,740 --> 00:14:59,660
What are you doing?

382
00:14:59,660 --> 00:15:00,460
Yu,

383
00:15:00,460 --> 00:15:02,260
she's obviously here to cause trouble.

384
00:15:02,460 --> 00:15:03,860
You don't have to
defend the Zhou family.

385
00:15:04,100 --> 00:15:05,740
I have to.
She's slandering the Zhou family.

386
00:15:06,860 --> 00:15:07,580
Enough.

387
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:08,540
Just stay here.

388
00:15:08,540 --> 00:15:09,340
I'll handle it.

389
00:15:38,780 --> 00:15:42,380
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

390
00:15:42,540 --> 00:15:45,740
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

391
00:15:46,260 --> 00:15:48,980
♪Who took the March rain♪

392
00:15:49,220 --> 00:15:52,580
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

393
00:15:52,940 --> 00:15:55,740
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

394
00:15:55,900 --> 00:15:59,100
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

395
00:15:59,980 --> 00:16:05,900
♪Needle and thread
stitch away the marks of time♪

396
00:16:05,940 --> 00:16:09,380
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

397
00:16:09,620 --> 00:16:12,460
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

398
00:16:12,620 --> 00:16:14,900
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

399
00:16:14,900 --> 00:16:19,100
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

400
00:16:19,180 --> 00:16:22,460
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

401
00:16:22,620 --> 00:16:25,740
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

402
00:16:26,260 --> 00:16:29,180
♪In this life I'd be a cloud-tailor♪

403
00:16:29,340 --> 00:16:35,860
♪Never failing the stars,
nor failing you♪

404
00:17:02,140 --> 00:17:05,660
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

405
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:09,060
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

406
00:17:09,660 --> 00:17:12,380
♪Who took the March rain♪

407
00:17:12,580 --> 00:17:15,900
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

408
00:17:16,300 --> 00:17:19,180
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

409
00:17:19,260 --> 00:17:22,980
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

410
00:17:23,020 --> 00:17:26,300
♪Warp and weft entwine,
one shuttle, one dream♪

411
00:17:26,300 --> 00:17:29,260
♪As seasons change♪

412
00:17:29,260 --> 00:17:32,900
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

413
00:17:32,900 --> 00:17:35,740
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

414
00:17:35,820 --> 00:17:38,380
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

415
00:17:38,380 --> 00:17:42,460
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

416
00:17:42,460 --> 00:17:45,780
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

417
00:17:45,780 --> 00:17:49,500
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

418
00:17:49,900 --> 00:17:53,020
♪Washing away
a lifetime of wear and tear♪

419
00:17:53,020 --> 00:17:55,900
♪Only for you♪

420
00:17:55,900 --> 00:17:59,500
♪On the street of golden honors,
the music rises♪

421
00:17:59,620 --> 00:18:02,380
♪The moon moves west
beyond the pavilion♪

422
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:05,060
♪Wine runs dry, yet the revelry lingers♪

423
00:18:05,060 --> 00:18:09,140
♪In silk, I seek a kindred soul♪

424
00:18:09,140 --> 00:18:12,460
♪The rain has ceased,
clouds begin to clear♪

425
00:18:12,500 --> 00:18:15,860
♪The fragrant silk billows
under the low-hung stars♪

426
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:22,380
♪I'd cut the clouds and morning glow
to drape over you♪

427
00:18:23,460 --> 00:18:27,580
♪A single bolt of silk becomes♪

428
00:18:28,860 --> 00:18:33,380
♪Your wedding gown♪
